And you first of all start doing that,

00:26:59.760 --> 00:27:01.880
otherwise children cannot do it.

00:27:02.200 --> 00:27:03.960
Now look at Christ,

00:27:04.080 --> 00:27:08.040
He lived hardly for four years,

00:27:08.120 --> 00:27:11.160
in the sense that He was out of

00:27:11.280 --> 00:27:13.200
that country.

