But when He was resurrected that made them think:

00:28:36.160 --> 00:28:39.160
''Who was He, and what He has done?

00:28:39.280 --> 00:28:42.160
How is it we are His disciples?''

00:28:42.240 --> 00:28:44.960
And they were ordinary fishermen,

00:28:45.080 --> 00:28:47.080
you know that very well,

00:28:47.160 --> 00:28:51.960
but their intelligence suddenly manifested,

00:28:52.080 --> 00:28:54.120
their dynamism manifested,

