00:29:12.200 --> 00:29:14.160
of Paul and Augustine,

00:29:14.240 --> 00:29:17.160
and that's how we see the problems of Christianity.

00:29:17.240 --> 00:29:20.080
So much so that we are shocked.

00:29:20.160 --> 00:29:24.080
How can Christianity of Christ would be like this?

00:29:24.120 --> 00:29:25.160
But it is,

